{"tid":1277252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六宗教領袖籲各方溝通 重回和平共融","createTime":"2019-07-02T06:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T07:04:49.000Z","uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4b0e633125c1dfbccd3325342aaadf3faafbd013","tid":1277252,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"大批示威者昨晚一度佔領立法會大樓，大樓多處造成破壞。本港<span style=\"color: red;\">佛教、天主教、孔教、伊斯蘭教、基督教及道教</span>領袖，發表聯合聲明表示深感痛心，呼籲政府、持不同立場及意見的人士，應放下執着，同謀香港大眾的福祉，令香港重回和平共融的軌道。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又呼籲香港市民抵制任何破壞法紀、損及和平及暴力傷害他人的行為，應以克己、理性、和平的手法表達意見。同時，亦希望各方能慎思自己的觀點，聆聽他人的聲音，盡快建立有效的溝通渠道，並以真誠的態度開展溝通。<br />\n<br />\n聲明強調，任何訴求不應與港人的福祉相違背，執着己見和對立只會令社會撕裂，無助解決目前困局，希望社會慎思淨慮，秉着開放、明智、包容及尊重的心，在溝通理解，顧己及人、尊重小我、共建大同的基礎上重新出發。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2179298/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2179298%2F&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=1229210e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2179298/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aab479a437075457ffb932a418ad252baf1a176","tid":1277252,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0277f440cbc083176d7591a9f7d92f334a81dfc8","tid":1277252,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef99adc33fd7d2678b14a80befec46a2c19db88","tid":1277252,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:54:26.000Z","msg":"六大派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"